N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 203.26 - Martin m. rosen

State Regulations

The Banking Board hereby grants permission for Martin M. Rosen to be a director of The Atlantic Bank of New York while president of

Model, Roland & Co., Inc., a New York stockbrokerage firm, chairman of The

First Washington Securities Corporation, investment bankers headquartered in

Washington, D.C. and chairman of First Washington International Corporation, located in New York and a member of the National Association of Securities

Dealers. Notes
